title: NFL Week 3 Fantasy/DFS Advice, Breakdown (Football 9/19)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Heath Cummings and Bryant McFadden to dish out fantasy football advice heading into Week 3 of the NFL season. But first, a historical/hypothetical debate on if the 2019 Dolphins would be legendary teams from decades ago. Then, fantasy! Will, Heath and Bryant discuss the injury impact of Ben Roethlisberger on the Steelers and Drew Brees on the Saints, whether Dak Prescott will finish as a top 3 fantasy QB and whether Daniel Jones will be fantasy relevant this year. Will and Heath finish with DFS tips heading into Week 3.
